CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1941, pg. 21 reads: "Danced In Barth Revue - Cute little Ernestine Pratt of Terrace Village danced in Mamie Barth's Revue at the Nixon Theatre last Wednesday. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Full length portrait of Ernestine Pratt wearing dark dance costume with ruffles around collar and skirt, posed with raised hand, in Harris Studio
